Print the adversary version

Usage:
  adversary version [flags]

Flags:
      --format string   output format: text or json (default "text")
  -h, --help            help for version
      --json            deprecated alias for --format json

Global Flags:
      --api-url string   Adversary Labs API endpoint (or ADVERSARY_API_URL) (default "https://adversarylabs.ai/api")
      --profile string   credential profile (default "default")
